events.title: two teenagers are gunned down on Lake Helena Road

movie.title: The Zodiac
movie.plot: An elusive serial killer known as the Zodiac terrorizes the San Francisco Bay in the late 1960s, while detectives aim to stop him before he claims more victims. Based on a true story.
